# LOTW replay fixture v1
# Format:
#   frame <count> [buttons...]
# Buttons use FCEUX joypad names: up down left right A B start select.
#
# This fixture waits for the title prompt, presses Start, and advances into the
# first controllable game state. It stores only controller timing, not ROM data
# or captured frames.
frame 300
frame 12 start
frame 108
